329/http://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/DEC/10_SF1/GCTPH1.ST16/0400000US34 |date=February 12, 2020 }}, [[United States Census Bureau]]. Accessed November 27, 2012.</ref>\n|population_density_sq_mi = 4290.0\n|population_density_km2   = auto\n|population_density_rank  = 138th of 566 in state<br>11th of 25 in county<ref name=GCTPH1NJ2010/>\n|population_est           = 100450\n|pop_est_as_of            = 2018\n|pop_est_footnotes        = <ref name=PopEst/>\n\n<!-- General information -->\n|timezone                 = [[Eastern Time Zone|Eastern (EST)]]\n|utc_offset               = &minus;5\n|timezone_DST             = [[Eastern Daylight Time|Eastern (EDT)]]\n|utc_offset_DST           = &minus;4\n|elevation_footnotes      = <ref name=\"GNIS\"/>\n|elevation_ft             = 59\n|elevation_m              = 18\n|coordinates              = {{coord|40.56|-74.29|region:US-NJ_type:city|display=inline,title}}\n|coordinates_footnotes    = <ref name=CensusArea/>\n\n<!-- Area/postal codes & others -->\n|postal_code_type         = [[ZIP Code]]s\n|postal_code              = 07001 - [[Avenel, New Jersey|Avenel]]<ref>[http://tools.usps.com/go/ZipLookupResultsAction!input.action?resultMode=0&city=avenel&state=NJ Look Up a ZIP Code for Avenel, NJ], [[United States Postal Service]]. Accessed March 19, 2012.</ref><br>07064 - [[Port Reading, New Jersey|Port Reading]]<ref>[http://tools.usps.com/go/ZipLookupResultsAction!input.action?resultMode=0&city=port%20reading&state=NJ Look Up a ZIP Code for Port Reading, NJ], [[United States Postal Service]]. Accessed March 19, 2012.</ref><br>07067 - [[Colonia, New Jersey|Colonia]]<ref>[http://tools.usps.com/go/ZipLookupResultsAction!input.action?resultMode=0&city=colonia&state=NJ Look Up a ZIP Code for Colonia, NJ], [[United States Postal Service]]. Accessed March 19, 2012.</ref><br>07077 - [[Sewaren, New Jersey|Sewaren]]<ref>[http://tools.usps.com/go/ZipLookupResultsAction!input.action?resultMode=0&city=sewaren&state=NJ Look Up a ZIP Code],